# events/ignore.conf — drop-filter for events you never want on the dashboard.
#
# Copy to events/ignore.conf (gitignored) and add patterns. An event is dropped
# if its TITLE matches ANY line here (OR), case-insensitively.
#
# Lines are shell-style globs:
#   *         matches any run of characters
#   ?         matches a single character
#   #-lines   and blank lines are ignored
# Everything else is matched literally (so ":" "(" "." etc. are fine as-is).
#
# Examples:
# HOLD:*            # drop placeholder "HOLD: ..." events
# *members only*    # drop anything flagged members-only
# *[CANCELLED]*     # drop titles literally containing [CANCELLED]
# Daily Standup*    # drop a recurring series you skip
